; NAME:
;  TEXTBOX
;
; PURPOSE:
;
;  This function allows the user to type some text in a
;  pop-up dialog widget and have it returned to the program.
;  This is an example of a Pop-Up Dialog Widget.
;
; AUTHOR:
;
;       FANNING SOFTWARE CONSULTING
